## Functional Requirements Details

### User Stories
- As a farmer, I want to check current crop prices so I can decide when to sell
- As a farmer, I want weather-aware recommendations so I can optimize my selling timing
- As a farmer, I want to query in natural language so I can get quick answers
- As an FPO, I want regional demand insights so I can plan better

### Acceptance Criteria
- Price API returns data within 1 second
- Recommendations include confidence scores
- Interface works on mobile devices
- AI assistant handles 80% of common queries

