## API Requirements

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant D as Data Layer
    participant A as AI Engine

    U->>F: Select crop & location
    F->>B: API Request
    B->>D: Fetch data
    D-->>B: Return data
    B->>A: Process with AI
    A-->>B: Generate insights
    B-->>F: Return response
    F-->>U: Display results
```